            <h3><b>Chantilly cream</b></h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Chill some double(heavy) and some milk in the refrigerator</li>
                <li>Mix the well-chilled cream with a third of its volume of very cold milk and whisk until frothy</li>
                <li>Add 6.5-7.5g caster sugar to each 500ml cram, flavour with vanilla extract</li>
                <li>Continue to whip until the ice cream remains in coils of the whisk </li>
                <li>Return to the refrigerator immediately until ready to use</li>
            </ul>
